title: National security adviser Jake Sullivan to meet with Chinese counterpart amid Ukraine invasion - CNN
content: National security adviser Jake Sullivan to meet with Chinese counterpart amid Ukraine invasion  CNNView Full Coverage on Google News
description: White House national security adviser Jake Sullivan will meet with his Chinese counterpart, Yang Jiechi, in Rome on Monday as part of a follow-up conversation to President Joe Biden and Chinese President Xi Jinping's virtual meeting last November, according to National Security Council spokesperson Emily Horne.
